document.full_text: tiger woods pulled out of the u.s. open on tuesday because of lingering issues with his left leg, leaving him uncertain how soon he can resume his pursuit of jack nicklaus' record for major titles.
document.title: tiger woods to skip u.s. open
lines_and_colors: tiger woods pulled out of the u.s. open on tuesday because of lingering issues with his left leg, leaving him uncertain how soon he can resume his pursuit of jack nicklaus' record for major titles.
